data.description: Golf course view embracing the active adult Westbrook Village lifestyle with your wonderful corner lot home! Enjoy the peaceful backyard overlooking the green, while under the large covered patio eating your freshly picked oranges from your backyard trees! The charming interior will surely amaze you, featuring vaulted ceilings, archways, plantation shutters, tile & carpet flooring,The large open living room & dining room, a family room with a fireplace & wet bar are designed for entertaining or relaxing! The bright kitchen is complete with built-in appliances, a convenient breakfast bar & eating area. Through the double doors is a large main bedroom with direct outdoor patio access, a bathroom with dual sinks, a large walk in shower & a walk-in closet.  What's not to like?
